data.title: Who's on Team USA? A List of the Athletes Qualified for the 2024 Paris Olympics
data.meta_description: Check out the ongoing list of athletes qualified for the 2024 Summer Games.
data.text:
With summer just around the corner, Olympic fans are gearing up to see their favorite athletes compete in Paris at the 2024 Summer Games, starting July 26. Before the torch is lit at the Opening Ceremony, get to know which athletes have qualified for the Games so far.

The U.S. Olympic Team roster includes over 500 athletes qualified to represent their home country in Paris this summer, according to NBC Sports. It will be one of the biggest representations of Team USA to date, and doesn't even include the list of alternates.

Team USA has announced which athletes have already been awarded their qualification.

RELATED: Revisiting the Legendary 1992 Dream Team and Their Gold-Medal Win at the Barcelona Olympics
